wear the clown suit.

03:16.400 --> 03:18.391
It's the last hoop, Tommy.

03:18.480 --> 03:22.075
You walk your beat, smile,
and you're officially out of the doghouse.

03:22.160 --> 03:23.673
One more day.

03:23.760 --> 03:27.070
Weather's gonna be nice, pretty girls,
fresh air, be like a big picnic.

03:27.160 --> 03:30.038
