11:34.600 --> 11:35.656
- All right.
- I'll see you tonight.

11:35.680 --> 11:36.749
Don't kick any cops.

11:36.880 --> 11:39.030
- I'll try not to.
- I hear they hate that.

11:51.880 --> 11:54.678
Sweetheart?
You saw me yesterday, right?

11:54.760 --> 11:57.877
- Woman: Mm-hmm.
- So, is it just me,

11:57.960 --> 11:59.856
